{"tid":2252072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局收到25宗涉警務人員子女被欺凌投訴及不滿個案","createTime":"2020-10-21T08:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T08:43:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3496bc8f36fb686afc65141cc70593e70ffc5b8f","tid":2252072,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"教育局表示，由去年6月至今，共收到25宗涉及警務人員子女在校園被欺凌的投訴及表達不滿的個案，學校已根據教育局的指引，向家長交代及輔導被欺凌學生，並已經對屬實個案的涉事教師及學生採取紀律行動，跟進調查涉事教師。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555937-20201021.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555937-20201021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=30ec15f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555937-20201021.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2276c442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555937-20201021.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}